New Westminster – A 46 year old man was arrested by Metro Vancouver Transit Police on Monday night after an alleged unprovoked hate motivated attack on a woman on the Canada Line.

At approximately 9:30 pm, December 4, 2017, a young woman boarded a Canada Line Train at Waterfront Station and sat down. A man seated nearby immediately stood up and allegedly began yelling at her as he walked towards her. He spoke in Arabic and allegedly hurled obscenities at her,
